{{MLBy|2009年}}霍尔持续低迷的状态，7月30日在对[[华盛顿国民|华盛顿国民]]的比赛后被下放至3A的[[纳什维尔天籁|纳什维尔天籁]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://milwaukee.brewers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090730&content_id=6143744&vkey=news_mil&fext=.jsp&c_id=mil | title = Struggling Hall sent down to Triple-A | date = 2009-07-30 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | publisher = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | author = Adam McCalvy | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615201254/http://milwaukee.brewers.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090730&content_id=6143744&vkey=news_mil&fext=.jsp&c_id=mil | archivedate = 2011年6月15日 | df =  }}</ref>。4天之后他就被叫回大联盟，取代受伤的[[科里·哈特|科里·哈特]]（[[:en:Corey_Hart_(baseball)|Corey Hart]]）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.jsonline.com/sports/brewers/52396537.html | title = Hall comes back full of confidence | publisher = 密尔沃基哨兵日报 | date = 2009-08-03 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | author = Anthony Witrado | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213119/http://www.jsonline.com/sports/brewers/52396537.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月12日霍尔被球队[[指定派遣|DFA]]，结束了长达7年的酿酒人生涯。

=== 西雅图水手 ===
{{MLBy|2009年}}8月19日霍尔被交易到[[西雅图水手|西雅图水手]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2009692780_mariners_acquire_bill_hall_fro.html?syndication=rss | title = Mariners acquire Bill Hall from Brewers | author = Geoff Baker | date = 2009-08-19 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | publisher = 西雅图时报 | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604092037/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2009692780_mariners_acquire_bill_hall_fro.html?syndication=rss | dead-url = no }}</ref>。来到水手的第一场比赛便击出两支安打和一分打点<ref>{{cite web | url = http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090821&content_id=6541124&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea | title = Wave of offense lifts Mariners to win | publisher = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | author = Steve Herrick | date = 2009-08-21 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100127202744/http://seattle.mariners.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090821&content_id=6541124&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=sea | archivedate = 2010年1月27日 | df =  }}</ref>。但这种状态未能持续下去，在水手队期间他的打击率仅有2成。

=== 波士顿红袜 ===
{{MLBy|2010年}}1月7日，霍尔被送到[[波士顿红袜|波士顿红袜]]，交易[[凯西·柯区曼|凯西·柯区曼]]和一名小联盟球员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100107&content_id=7888070&vkey=news_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos | title = Seattle acquires Kotchman, adds to makeover | date = 2010-01-07 | accessdate = 2010-01-25 | publisher = [[MLB.com|MLB.com]] | author = Doug Miller | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100111092932/http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100107&content_id=7888070&vkey=news_bos&fext=.jsp&c_id=bos | archivedate = 2010-01-11 }}</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
除了棒球外，霍尔还喜欢的运动还有[[高尔夫|高尔夫]]和[[台球|台球]]，另外他还喜欢电子游戏，最喜欢的电影是疤面煞星，最喜欢的音乐类型是[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]和[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]，[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的[[洛斯卡波斯|洛斯卡波斯]]是他最喜欢的度假地点。

他和前队友[[J·J·哈迪|J·J·哈迪]]、[[杰夫·苏潘|杰夫·苏潘]]、[[克里斯·卡普亚诺|克里斯·卡普亚诺]]（[[:en:Chris_Capuano|Chris Capuano]]）曾在[[哥伦比亚广播公司|CBS]]的肥皂剧[[年轻和骚动不安的一族|年轻和骚动不安的一族]]中客串过角色。

